name: Cynet Storm
desc: Linked monsters on the field gain 500 ATK/DEF. The Link Summon of Link Monsters cannot be negated. If you take 2000 or more damage by battle or a card effect: You can shuffle the face-down cards in your Extra Deck and excavate the top card of those cards, and if it is a Cyberse Link Monster, Special Summon it. Otherwise, return it to its original position.
